0:{"buildId":"I3GEKSVLVTWqxcEXDRaWq","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"What is the difference between OHSAS 18001 and ISO 45001?"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:32:13+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"Compare ohsas 18001 and iso 45001: difference between 18001 and 45001 is listed. Checkout the article."}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"What is the difference between OHSAS 18001 and ISO 45001?"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO certification in Dubai like ISO 18001 and ISO 45001 certifications may sound the same but it is not. The most important difference between ISO 45001 and OHSAS 18001 is the structure. 45001 have adopted the Annex SL High Level Structure. This structure is followed by most of the latest ISO standards like ISO 9001 and 14001."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The context has to be systematically determined and monitored. Context can be internal or external. The organization has to determine external and internal context that affects the organization and its Occupational health and safety (OH&S) management system. This context can be positive or negative."}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"OHSAS 18001 standard is the British standard for occupational health and safety management whereas ISO 45001 is standard for occupational health and safety management published by International Organization for standardization (ISO)."}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 45001 standard is compatible with ISO 14001:2015 and ISO 9001:2015. Thus choosing this management system will increase the health and safety of the organization. Whereas OHSAS 18001 is not compatible with ISO 14001 and ISO 9001."}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 45001 does proactive planning to mitigate the risks whereas OHSAS 18001 is a relative old standard and does reactive planning to mitigate risks of an organization."}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"OHSAS 18001 focuses on controlling the hazard whereas ISO 45001 focuses on how evaluation, reduction and prevention of risks can be done."}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"In OHSAS 18001 procedures are prepared for identification and controlling the hazard. Documented results are required for risk mitigation."}],["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Management of the company reviews the process after development is done under OHSAS 18001. Senior management is expected to take the leadership role in driving performance improvements into action and taking responsibility for safety of the employees. Under OHSAS 18001 the operation of occupational health and safety is carried out by safety management representative. Whereas in ISO 45001 top management plays the leadership role"}],"$L2","$L3","$L4","$L5","$L6"]}],"$L7"]}]}],["$L8"],"$L9"]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
2:["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"OHSAS 18001 is a management standard that ignored workers interests. In ISO 45001 workers can participate broadly and work with the management to implement safety management system. ISO 45001 allows participation of workers to a greater degree in occupational health and safety management."}]
3:["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"In ISO 45001, increased focus is given on the planning and determination of objectives by an organization. This is done to asses and evaluates the achievements of the employee during performance review. ISO 45001 is more explicit than OHSAS 18001 in formalizing the objectives of the organization, supporting organizational health and safety policy and establishing documentation."}]
4:["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 45001 deals with risks and opportunities both whereas OHSAS 18001 exclusively deal with Risks. ISO 45001 encourages risk based thinking. ISO 45001 has a section to tackle emergency situations."}]
5:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 45001 includes the views of interested parties whereas OHSAS 18001 does not include views of interested parties.ISO 45001 is dynamic in all its clauses but OHSAS 18001 is not dynamic in its clauses."}]
6:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Wizms offer ISO 45001 certification consulting services in Dubai, Sharjah, Ajman, Al Ain, Fujairah, Abu Dhabi, and Ras al-Khaimah."}]
7:["$","footer",null,{"className":"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"iso 45001 vs ohsas 18001"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"difference between iso 45001 and ohsas 18001"}],["$","span","2",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"difference between 18001 and 45001"}],["$","span","3",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"difference between ohsas 18001 and iso 14001"}],["$","span","4",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"iso 18001 vs 45001"}],["$","span","5",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"what is the difference between ohsas 18001 and iso 45001"}],["$","span","6",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"iso 18001 vs iso"}]]}]}]
